            <title><![CDATA[Infinity Nikki ‘Behind-the-Scenes: The Grand Millewish Tree Silently Grows’ documentary]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2024/11/infinity-nikki-behind-the-scenes-the-grand-millewish-tree-silently-grows-documentary</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/infinity-nikki-%E2%80%98behind-the-scenes-the-grand-millewish-tree-silently-grows%E2%80%99-documentary.1041381/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gematsu.com/2024/11/infinity-nikki-behind-the-scenes-the-grand-millewish-tree-silently-grows-documentary<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/mobile/smartphone">Smartphone</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>An in-depth look at the development process.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Infold Games [8 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/papergames/infold-games">Infold Games</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Papergames [12 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/papergames">Papergames</a> have released a 25-minute behind-the-scenes documentary for <a title="Genres > Free-to-Play [335 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/free-to-play">free-to-play</a> <a title="Genres > Open-World [514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/open-world">open-world</a> dress-up <a title="Genres > Adventure [1,878 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/adventure">adventure game</a> <em><a title="Games > Infinity Nikki [7 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/infinity-nikki">Infinity Nikki</a></em> titled “The Grand Millewish Tree <a title="Companies > Sile" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sile">Sile</a>ntly Grows.” <span id="more-929171"></span></p><p>“At the heart of the Wishing Woods stands the largest and oldest tree in this area—the Grand Millewish Tree,” reads the documentary description. “It’s the home of Faewish Sprites, descendants of the Wishing One. The Grand Millewish Tree is a microcosm of the Miraland’s ecology, and also carries the heartfelt wishes of the <em>Infinity Nikki</em> development team. Through countless days and nights, this tree has quietly sprouted, growing endlessly. Welcome to Miraland! We hope you enjoy yourself in this world!”</p><p><em>Infinity Nikki</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [8,399 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > PC [21,747 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via client download and <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/infinity-nikki-71fc64?lang=en-US" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Epic Games Store</a>, iOS via <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/infinity-nikki/id6502622570" target="_blank" rel="noopener">App Store</a>, and Android via <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.infoldgames.infinitynikkien" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Play</a> on December 5.</p><p>Watch the documentary below.</p><h2><span>Behind-the-Scenes: The Grand Millewish Tree Silently Grows</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><iframe title="Infinity Nikki A Behind-the-Scenes: The Grand Millewish Tree Silently Grows" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/U174KpovT_E?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="『インフィニティニキ』千願の大樹 開発ドキュメンタリー" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/y11CqDABXE0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Traditional Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe title="《無限暖暖》千願巨樹幕後製作紀錄片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hNq-L2HH90s?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Neko Odyssey launches December 16]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2024/11/neko-odyssey-launches-december-16</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/neko-odyssey-launches-december-16.1041354/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gematsu.com/2024/11/neko-odyssey-launches-december-16<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Demo updated with prologue.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Cat photography casual <a title="Genres > Adventure [1,878 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/adventure">adventure game</a> <em><a title="Games > Neko Odyssey [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/neko-odyssey">Neko Odyssey</a></em> will launch for <a title="Platforms > PC [21,747 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2476350/Neko_Odyssey/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Steam</a> on December 16 for $19.99 / €19.50 / 2,200 yen, publisher <a title="Companies > Flyhigh Works [158 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/flyhigh-works">Flyhigh Works</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Secret Character [5 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/secret-character">Secret Character</a> announced. <span id="more-928621"></span></p><p>The currently available demo has also been updated, adding a prologue that shows how protagonist came Miki to visit the island with a secret to live with her aunt.</p><p>Here is an overview of the game, via its <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2476350/Neko_Odyssey/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Steam page</a>:</p><blockquote><p><em>Neko Odyssey</em> is a game for cat lovers you can’t miss!</p><p>Here’s a slightly unusual casual adventure game where the main gameplay centers around taking pictures of cats. The pixel art graphics in a 3D setting create a charming atmosphere reminiscent of Japanese animation.</p><p>In the game, you’ll have to search for cats in various locations throughout the town and take pictures to upload to social media (in game). Each photo you upload will earn likes from netizens. As you receive more likes, you’ll become better known, and your followers may offer tips on finding new and different cat poses.</p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p>During the cat photography sessions, some cats may require you to establish a connection with them before allowing you to photograph them. You’ll also encounter certain events that will lead you to discover new photo opportunities.</p><p>Apart from taking cat photos and sharing them on social media, the game features a main storyline where you’ll unravel the mysteries of the town based on the information you capture in your cat photos. You’ll experience excitement, cuteness, and inspiration along with the adventure in this game.</p></blockquote><p>Watch a new trailer below. View a new set of screenshots <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/gallery/neko-odyssey/november-20-2024/">at the gallery</a>.</p><h2><span>Release Date Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="Neko Odyssey - Release Date Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/H2efGweM2JI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><h2><span>Screenshots</span></h2><div id="carousel_928626"><ul><li><span>❮</span></li><li><span>❯</span></li></ul></div></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Dragon Quest III HD-2D Remake details mysterious dungeons]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2024/11/dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d-remake-details-mysterious-dungeons</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d-remake-details-mysterious-dungeons.1041348/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gematsu.com/2024/11/dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d-remake-details-mysterious-dungeons<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Venture within to fight formidable foes.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Square Enix [5,313 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/square-enix">Square Enix</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Artdink Corporation [34 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/artdink-corporation">Artdink Corporation</a> have released new information for <em><a title="Games > Dragon Quest III HD-2D Remake [13 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d-remake">Dragon Quest III HD-2D Remake</a></em>, teasing some of the more formidable foes that await within mysterious dungeons. <span id="more-929134"></span></p><p>Get the details below.</p><blockquote><p><strong>Mysterious Dungeons Aplenty Await on Your Travels</strong></p><p>While adventuring, you will come across dungeons shrouded in mystery from time to time. Venture within and you might find them to be surprisingly large and home to some formidable foes. If you’re lucky, treasure or unexpected encounters may await as well. Explore till you can explore no more!</p><p><em>—What’s this? A cave surrounded by clouds on all sides!?</em></p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dragon-Quest-III-HD-2D-Remake_2024_11-20-24_001.jpg"></a></figure><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><em>—While exploring this area, you’ll come face-to-face with strong monsters you’ve never fought before!</em></p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dragon-Quest-III-HD-2D-Remake_2024_11-20-24_002.jpg"></a></figure><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dragon-Quest-III-HD-2D-Remake_2024_11-20-24_003.jpg"></a></figure><p><em>—Upon exiting the cave you suddenly find yourself in a…castle. What’s a castle doing here?</em></p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dragon-Quest-III-HD-2D-Remake_2024_11-20-24_004.jpg"></a></figure><p><em>—A tower that seems to touch the sky itself.</em></p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dragon-Quest-III-HD-2D-Remake_2024_11-20-24_005.jpg"></a></figure><p><em>—Even mightier enemies block your path!</em></p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dragon-Quest-III-HD-2D-Remake_2024_11-20-24_006.jpg"></a></figure><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dragon-Quest-III-HD-2D-Remake_2024_11-20-24_007.jpg"></a></figure><p><em>—What awaits after meeting this curious creature?</em></p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dragon-Quest-III-HD-2D-Remake_2024_11-20-24_008.jpg"></a></figure><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dragon-Quest-III-HD-2D-Remake_2024_11-20-24_009.jpg"></a></figure></blockquote><p><em>Dragon Quest III HD-2D Remake</em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [8,399 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [6,383 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [16,331 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [21,747 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2701660/DRAGON_QUEST_III_HD2D_Remake/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Steam</a> and <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d-remake/9n80pq2dsbp1" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Microsoft Store</a> on November 14 worldwide. Read more about the game <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/07/dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d-remake-details-story-protagonist-world-spells-and-abilities">here</a>, <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/08/dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d-remake-details-new-episodes-world">here</a>, <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/09/dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d-remake-details-parties-vocations-and-monster-arenas">here</a>, and <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/10/dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d-remake-details-monster-arena-tournaments-rescuing-monsters-and-more-locations">here</a>.</p><p>View a new set of screenshots <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/gallery/dragon-quest-iii-hd-2d-remake/november-20-2024/">at the gallery</a>.</p><h2><span>Screenshots</span></h2><div id="carousel_929135"><ul><li><span>❮</span></li><li><span>❯</span></li></ul></div></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
